fulltitle: CHICK COREA - Renowned Pianist-Composer & 22-time Grammy winner - ARTIST SERIES
title: CHICK COREA - Renowned Pianist-Composer & 22-time Grammy winner - ARTIST SERIES
description:
"Happiness is Music" and Chick's talent, style & music has made millions happy for over 5 decades. Hear about his heroes & inspiration in this industry, his mentors to success & tips of learning.  What musician changed him forever? Creating something of quality to a listener, "Simple thing called communication" is a factor in his performance.  Always learning, keep going forward....keys to success!
The Sessions Panel & our Artist Series interviews with Dom Famularo share music industry knowledge to musicians worldwide!!  The panel events include Entertainment Law, Marketing, Networking, Artist Relations & Motivational skills and experiences from professionals and experts who have been "on the road" and are successful in the industry.  The interviews share tips, exclusive background information from Artists in the music industry and the importance of knowing music history.
